OL,3,CBritain's most southerly post office
OL,4,Cset to close
OL,6,FIt's famously known as mainland
OL,7,FBritain's most southerly post office,
OL,8,Fbut the future of the Lizard village
OL,9,Fbranch is now uncertain.
OL,11,FTenants Ken and Linda Trott have
OL,12,Fdecided to retire after running the
OL,13,Fhistoric post office for nearly 40
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FThe premises are for sale, but the
OL,17,Fcouple have struggled to find anyone
OL,18,Felse to take on their much-loved
OL,19,Fbusiness.
