OL,3,CBritain's most southerly post office
OL,4,Cset to close
OL,6,FKen Trott told ITV News: "There's so
OL,7,Fmuch history. It's been a post office
OL,8,Fsince 1898, there's a lot of history
OL,9,Ftied in the place.
OL,11,F"It'll be really sad for it to stop."
OL,13,FAt almost 80, Ken says recent health
OL,14,Fproblems have meant the job is too
OL,15,Ftiring and the time has come for the
OL,16,Fcouple to stop working.
OL,18,FHe said: "It's very much bittersweet.
OL,19,FI love the job, I loved the work until
OL,20,Fvery recently, until I started finding
OL,21,Fit a struggle, really."
