OL,6,FLinda says it will be a sad day when
OL,7,Fthey close.
OL,9,F"I've got mixed feelings about going,"
OL,10,Fshe said. "It's quite emotional. We've
OL,11,Fbeen here for so long, it's quite hard
OL,12,Fto let it go."
OL,14,FThe historic branch is full of postal
OL,15,Fantiques that Ken likes to use when
OL,16,Fserving customers.
