OL,6,F"I've still got some very old balance
OL,7,Fscales that I use for weighing bundles
OL,8,Fof notes and comparing weight on
OL,9,Fairmail letters and so on," he said.
OL,10,F"It's just nice using the old stuff."
OL,12,FA Post Office spokesperson said: "Len
OL,13,Fand Linda Trott have served The Lizard
OL,14,Fcommunity for 36 years.
OL,16,F"They have now decided to take a well-
OL,17,Fearned retirement. We want to
OL,18,Fsincerely thank this couple for their
OL,19,Flong and loyal service and for going
OL,20,Fabove and beyond for their customers.
